@startuml
[*] --> RegisteredOrLoggedIn : register or login with details

RegisteredOrLoggedIn --> Teacher : continue as teacher
RegisteredOrLoggedIn --> Student : continue as student

Teacher --> CreateQuiz : create new quiz [quiz not created]
CreateQuiz --> QuizCreated : quiz created [quiz saved]

Teacher --> EditQuiz : edit existing quiz [quiz exists]
EditQuiz --> QuizEdited : quiz edited [quiz saved]

Teacher --> SaveDraft : save quiz as draft [quiz saved]
SaveDraft --> DraftSaved : draft saved

Teacher --> ViewResults : view quiz results [results available]

Student --> SelectQuiz : select a quiz after notification [quiz selected]
SelectQuiz --> Answering : answer the selected quiz [answers submitted]

Answering --> SubmitQuiz : submit quiz [quiz submitted]
SubmitQuiz --> QuizSubmitted : quiz submitted

Student --> ViewResult : view result after submitting quiz [result available]
@enduml
